name: Like-General
description: Like [quantity] object(s)
rules: {"sql":"select (case when ((a.a + b.b) >= 1) then 1 else 0 end ) as flag from (select count(*) as a from posts p , likes l where l.facebook_user_id != p.facebook_user_id && l.post_id = p.post_id &&l.fanpage_id = p.fanpage_id && l.facebook_user_id = :facebook_user_id && l.fanpage_id = :fanpage_id && l.likes=1) as a,  ( select count(*) as b from likes l , comments c where l.facebook_user_id != c.facebook_user_id && l.post_id = c.comment_id && l.fanpage_id = c.fanpage_id && l.facebook_user_id = :facebook_user_id && l.fanpage_id = :fanpage_id && l.likes=1 ) as b"}

rules: {"sql":"select (case when ((a.a + b.b) >= 1000) then 1 else 0 end ) as flag from  (select count(*) as a from posts p , likes l   where l.facebook_user_id != p.facebook_user_id && l.post_id = p.post_id && l.fanpage_id = p.fanpage_id && l.facebook_user_id = :facebook_user_id &&  l.fanpage_id = :fanpage_id &&(l.created_time - interval 1 minute) < p.created_time && l.likes=1  ) as a,  ( select count(*) as b from likes l , comments c where l.facebook_user_id != c.facebook_user_id && l.post_id = c.comment_id && l.fanpage_id = c.fanpage_id && l.facebook_user_id = :facebook_user_id && l.fanpage_id = :fanpage_id &&(l.created_time - interval 1 minute) < c.created_time  && l.likes=1 ) as b"}

rules: {"sql":"select (case when (a.a  >= 50) then 1 else 0 end ) as flag from(select count(*) as a from posts p , likes l where l.facebook_user_id != p.facebook_user_id && l.post_id = p.post_id && l.fanpage_id = p.fanpage_id && l.facebook_user_id = :facebook_user_id && l.fanpage_id = :fanpage_id && p.post_type='link' && (l.created_time - interval 1 minute) < p.created_time && l.likes=1) as a"}

rules: {"sql":"select (case when (a.a  >= 25) then 1 else 0 end ) as flag from (select count(*) as a from comments c, posts p  where c.facebook_user_id = :facebook_user_id && c.fanpage_id = :fanpage_id && p.fanpage_id = c.fanpage_id && c.comment_post_id = p.post_id && c.comment_type = 'status' &&(c.created_time - interval 1 minute) < p.created_time) as a "}

name: Get-Like-General
description: Get [quantity] like(s) on a post
rules: {"sql":"select (case when ((a.a + b.b) >= 1) then 1 else 0 end ) as flag from (select count(*) as a from posts p , likes l   where l.facebook_user_id != p.facebook_user_id && l.post_id = p.post_id && l.fanpage_id = p.fanpage_id && p.facebook_user_id = :facebook_user_id && p.fanpage_id = :fanpage_id ) as a, ( select count(*) as b from likes l , comments c where l.facebook_user_id != c.facebook_user_id && l.post_id = c.comment_id && l.fanpage_id = c.fanpage_id && c.facebook_user_id = :facebook_user_id && c.fanpage_id = :fanpage_id ) as b"}

name: Get-Like-General-10sec
description: Get [quantity] like(s) on a post within 10 seconds of Posting Time
rules: {"sql":"select (case when ((a.a + b.b) >= 1) then 1 else 0 end ) as flag from (select count(*) as a from posts p , likes l   where l.facebook_user_id != p.facebook_user_id && l.post_id = p.post_id && l.fanpage_id = p.fanpage_id && p.facebook_user_id = :facebook_user_id && p.fanpage_id = :fanpage_id && (l.created_time - interval 10 second) < p.created_time) as a, ( select count(*) as b from likes l , comments c where l.facebook_user_id != c.facebook_user_id && l.post_id = c.comment_id && l.fanpage_id = c.fanpage_id && c.facebook_user_id = :facebook_user_id && c.fanpage_id = :fanpage_id && (l.created_time - interval 10 second) < c.created_time) as b"}

rules: {"sql":"select (case when ((a.a + b.b) >= 10) then 1 else 0 end ) as flag from (select count(*) as a from posts p , likes l   where l.facebook_user_id != p.facebook_user_id && l.post_id = p.post_id && l.fanpage_id = p.fanpage_id && p.facebook_user_id = :facebook_user_id && p.fanpage_id = :fanpage_id && (l.created_time - interval 1 minute) < p.created_time) as a, ( select count(*) as b from likes l , comments c where l.facebook_user_id != c.facebook_user_id && l.post_id = c.comment_id && l.fanpage_id = c.fanpage_id && c.facebook_user_id = :facebook_user_id && c.fanpage_id = :fanpage_id && (l.created_time - interval 1 minute) < c.created_time) as b"}

rules: {"sql":"select (case when (a.a  >= 10) then 1 else 0 end ) as flag from (select count(*) as a from posts p , likes l   where l.facebook_user_id != p.facebook_user_id && l.post_id = p.post_id && l.fanpage_id = p.fanpage_id && p.facebook_user_id = :facebook_user_id && p.fanpage_id = :fanpage_id &&p.post_type = 'status' && (l.created_time - interval 1 minute) < p.created_time) as a"}
